	<h1 class="title">再也不用“剁手”了，在淘宝花的钱可以拿来买万科的房子</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-26 11:13:45 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2024/medium/2024.jpg?1436647412" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="2024" data-title="《再也不用“剁手”了，在淘宝花的钱可以拿来买万科的房子》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2024/medium/2024.jpg?1436647412" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2024.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
